Line13.D5161: He caught me robbing ships in Gea Kul. (scoff) I was barely old enough to shave.
Line15.D5161: By law, he should've cut off my hand, but he brought me to Dahlgur instead. Made me an Iron Wolf.
Line17.D5161: Well... it was Captain Haddad’s fault.
MenuLabel: “How did you become an Iron Wolf?”
VoiceDir17.D5161: Grinning. Knows he's a pain in Haddad's ass.
